data.meta_description: Pooja Sharma is an Indian model and actress known for the role of Draupadi in Star Plus's Mahabharat and as Mahakali / Parvati in Colors TV's Mahakali - Anth Hi Aarambh Hai. DuringÂ the beginning of her career, she did a sports-based talk show for Doordarshan. She also worked in shows RadhaKrishn, Ram Siya Ke Luv Kush as narrator. She has appeared in a couple of Hindu mythological shows.
